{"id":178,"parent_id":172,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":178,"title":"Galatians 6","subtitle":"","short_title":"Gal.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 6"],[".studySummary",["i","Bear one another’s burdens—As you sow, so shall you reap—Be not weary in well-doing."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.1","order":"03.11.006.19854"},["b","1"],"Brethren, if a man be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"overtaken"],"in a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"fault"],", ye which are spiritual,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"restore"],"such an one in the spirit of meekness;",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"considering"],"thyself, lest thou also be tempted."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.2","order":"03.11.006.19855"},["b","2"],"Bear ye one another’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"burdens"],", and so fulfil the law of Christ."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.3","order":"03.11.006.19856"},["b","3"],"For if a man think himself to be something, when he is nothing, he deceiveth himself."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.4","order":"03.11.006.19857"},["b","4"],"But let every man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"prove"],"his own",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"work"],", and then shall he have rejoicing in himself alone, and not in another."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.5","order":"03.11.006.19858"},["b","5"],"For every man shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"bear"],"his own burden."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.6","order":"03.11.006.19859"},["b","6"],"Let him that is taught in the word",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"communicate"],"unto him that teacheth in all good things."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.7","order":"03.11.006.19860"},["b","7"],"Be not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"deceived"],"; God is not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"mocked"],": for whatsoever a man",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"soweth"],", that shall he also",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"reap"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.8","order":"03.11.006.19861"},["b","8"],"For he that soweth to his flesh shall of the flesh reap corruption; but he that soweth to the Spirit shall of the Spirit reap life everlasting."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.9","order":"03.11.006.19862"},["b","9"],"And let us not be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"weary"],"in well doing: for in due season we shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"reap"],", if we faint not."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.10","order":"03.11.006.19863"},["b","10"],"As we have therefore opportunity, let us do",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"good"],"unto all",["i","men,"],"especially unto them who are of the household of faith."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.11","order":"03.11.006.19864"},["b","11"],"Ye see how large a letter I have written unto you with mine own hand."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.12","order":"03.11.006.19865"},["b","12"],"As many as desire to make a fair shew in the flesh, they constrain you to be circumcised; only lest they should suffer",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"persecution"],"for the cross of Christ."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.13","order":"03.11.006.19866"},["b","13"],"For neither they themselves who are circumcised keep the law; but desire to have you circumcised, that they may glory in your flesh."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.14","order":"03.11.006.19867"},["b","14"],"But God forbid that I should glory, save in the cross of our Lord Jesus Christ, by whom the world is crucified unto me, and I unto the world."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.15","order":"03.11.006.19868"},["b","15"],"For in Christ Jesus neither",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"circumcision"],"availeth any thing, nor uncircumcision, but a new creature."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.16","order":"03.11.006.19869"},["b","16"],"And as many as walk according to this rule,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"peace"],["i","be"],"on them, and mercy, and upon the Israel of God."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.17","order":"03.11.006.19870"},["b","17"],"From henceforth let no man trouble me: for I bear in my body the marks of the Lord Jesus."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.18","order":"03.11.006.19871"},["b","18"],"Brethren, the grace of our Lord Jesus Christ",["i","be"],"with your spirit. Amen."]],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal.closing.4","order":".000.19910"},[".closing","¶Unto the Galatians written from Rome."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.1a","order":"03.11.006.19872"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/14.1"},"Rom. 14:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.80"},"D&C 20:80"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.1b","order":"03.11.006.19874"},["b","1b"],["span.small","GR"],"transgression, trespass."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.1c","order":"03.11.006.19876"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/12.13"},"Heb. 12:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.1d","order":"03.11.006.19878"},["b","1d"],["span.small","GR"],"watching."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.2a","order":"03.11.006.19880"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/compassion"},"TG Compassion"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.4a","order":"03.11.006.19882"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"TG Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.4b","order":"03.11.006.19884"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/good-works"},"TG Good Works"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.5a","order":"03.11.006.19886"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/9.12"},"Prov. 9:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.6a","order":"03.11.006.19888"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/communication"},"TG Communication"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.7a","order":"03.11.006.19890"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deceit"},"TG Deceit"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.7b","order":"03.11.006.19892"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mocking"},"TG Mocking"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.7c","order":"03.11.006.19894"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/32.27"},"Ezek. 32:27"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/accountability"},"TG Accountability"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/agency"},"Agency"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/good-works"},"Good Works"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.7d","order":"03.11.006.19896"},["b","7d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/7.16"},"Ps. 7:16"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/harvest"},"TG Harvest"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.9a","order":"03.11.006.19898"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/8.14.14-15"},"Luke 8:14 (14–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.13"},"2 Thes. 3:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.33"},"D&C 64:33"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/steadfastness"},"TG Steadfastness"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.9b","order":"03.11.006.19900"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/abundant-life"},"TG Abundant Life"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.10a","order":"03.11.006.19902"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/3.27"},"Prov. 3:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/gal/6.12a","order":"03.11.006.19904"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"h